text: Olga Rajković (born 13 April 1913, date of death unknown) was a Yugoslav gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Yugoslav female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
